data.description: Welcome to 105 Partridge Drive in  beautiful Kenwood Hills Russell, KY! This stunning home offers everything you need and more. With 5 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 baths, there's plenty of room for the whole the main floor has 2 living areas each with a gas log fire place, an office and dining room.The large kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with a pantry for all your storage needs.The 3-car garage provides ample space for parking and storage, and the walk-up attic offers even more room for your belongings. There’s even an EV charger! The master bedroom is a true oasis, featuring a luxurious bathroom ensuite with a walk-in closet, & gaslog fp. You'll love unwinding in this private retreat after a long day. The finished walk-out basement is perfect for entertaining, with a bar and kitchenette that will impress your guests. There’s also a gas log fireplace, and 2 extra rooms for bedrooms or a gym. And finally Step outside onto the covered deck grill and watch the kids play  in your fenced-in backyard. Don't miss your chance to own this incredible home!
